3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a decentralized protocol for maintaining network connectivity, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with network connectivity and protocols for maintaining it, which is a topic within the domain of networking and internet architecture.
